{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Automate a team of robots to gather resources, reshape terrain, and scale up factories on a procedurally generated alien world.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore a procedural world</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every game you are exploring a different planet, with a different set of resources and biomes that present unique challenge. You start able to only see a small area, but as you progress you build out a radio network and unlock more of the world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613890/extras/Montage.gif?t=1738615642\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Collect resources</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Expanding your colony requires ever increasing quantity of resources. Luckily, the planet you're on is ripe with them to find and use. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613890/extras/Mine2.gif?t=1738615642\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Programming</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Anything you can do you can automate. It becomes a necessity as your colony grows larger, and recipes get more complex. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613890/extras/UIGIF.gif?t=1738615642\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Single-player colony-builder</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Automatable robots and factories</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Procedurally generated voxel world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Mutable terrain</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> An easy-to-learn visual scripting language</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Sharable scripts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Fog-of-war and power mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Crafti